  "texts": [
    "These retrieved chunks are then combined with the input query to generate the prompt, which is sent to the LLM to generate the output.",
    "Finally, the crafted prompt, derived from the previous stage, is fed into the fine-tuned LLM, which generates an answer containing grounded information concerning the process model.In the following, we provide an in-depth discussion of each phase within the overall process.",
    "From a technological standpoint, the backbone of the pipeline was realized by leveraging the Langchain frameworkfoot_0.",
